This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=4420

This script look for some keywords on licenses, identify a license block in the start of a file, and folds it. 

The license can be commented in the following styles:
C single line
C multi line
bash single line

it should be fair easy to add other comment styles.

fork it at https://github.com/fotanus/fold_license






